extends androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<ConfigurationsListAdapter.ConfigsViewHolder>

        public void setFoodItems(List<? extends FoodItem> newFoodItems)
        Sets the list of food-items that functions as a data source for this adapter. If already set, calculates an optimal set of update operations to migrate from the old list to the new one.
